PROJECT 2
Sales & Marketing Dashboard

Overview
-----------
This project is an interactive Sales & Marketing Dashboard built using Power BI. It provides comprehensive insights into sales performance,
customer demographics, and marketing campaign effectiveness. Designed to help sales and marketing teams make data-driven decisions through dynamic visualizations and KPIs.

Key Features
------------
    KPI Cards – for Total Sales, Total Profit, Avg Discount, Total Leads, and Conversion Rate
    Line Chart – Sales and Profit over Time
    Bar Chart – Top 5 Selling Products
    Map/Bar Chart – Sales by Region
    Funnel Chart – Marketing Funnel (Leads to Conversions)

Tools & Technologies
-----------------------

    Power BI Desktop
    DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)
    CSV Datasets
   .pbit Template File

DAX MEASURES
-------------
Total Sales = SUM(Sales_Data[Sales])
Total Profit = SUM(Sales_Data[Profit])
Average Discount = AVERAGE(Sales_Data[Discount])
Total Leads = SUM(Campaign_Data[Leads])
Conversion Rate = 
    DIVIDE(SUM(Campaign_Data[Conversions]), SUM(Campaign_Data[Leads]))
